{"tid":1298341,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[推] 玩膠事件入黎將功補過!!!  不割席 不亂捉鬼","createTime":"2019-07-09T00:32:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T07:05:33.000Z","uid":105976,"like":87,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"600cc1bf61375845bcf586f834ab3e71fcb65295","tid":1298341,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T00:32:11.000Z","msg":"大家記唔記得雨革後期係點散<br />\n高登成頁都係互相指責POST  邊個係鬼 邊個係熱狗  個個都冇晒動力繼續落去<br />\n<br />\n被玩係好嬲 但玩膠既人絕大部份都係同路人  只係一時衰on9<br />\n出發點係好既 想令狗狗疲於奔命  點知玩到自已人<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">點都好 而家將功補過  推有用文宣<br />\n幫手用template send信   未課金既快課<br />\n希望琴晚被玩既義士們原諒佢地</span></strong><br />\n個個都會犯錯  好似話圍TVB咁 可能都係一時諗得唔夠周詳<br />\n講左原因 大家討論左結果 唔洗罵係鬼   <br />\n如果因為咁唔再出黎 又割席又捉鬼  整整下好快就冇晒人<br />\n大家要繼續團結  加油<br />\n<br />\n【 Template Ready】白色恐怖下，一定要向監警會、醫管局算帳還拖！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1287962/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1287962/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n表態反對DQ確認書：炸爆選管會電郵 (附template)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1282439/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1282439/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n美國page 教人幫手推美國通過法案<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1283300/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1283300/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n雲海開班教投訴<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1290737/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1290737/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n消費前，睇下呢個地圖！斷親共收入！<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2IKNf97\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2IKNf97&d=Xf5vvBv8GY7fsWMyNBE0dtagwJJ%2BwSr9lfhZhsTZPo0%3D&h=eb37f657\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2IKNf97</a><br />\n<br />\n6.9-7.7克警資料整合<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1295376/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1295376/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n課金支持:<br />\n立場新聞<br />\n<a href=\"https://mystand.thestandnews.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmystand.thestandnews.com%2F&d=Xf5vvBv8GY7fsWMyNBE0dtagwJJ%2BwSr9lfhZhsTZPo0%3D&h=b454f6f4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmystand.thestandnews.com%2F&h=f3bb6897\" target=\"_blank\">https://mystand.thestandnews.com/</a><br />\n<br />\n傳真社<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.factwire.org/backus/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.factwire.org%2Fbackus%2F&d=Xf5vvBv8GY7fsWMyNBE0dtagwJJ%2BwSr9lfhZhsTZPo0%3D&h=6d2e9d9f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.factwire.org/backus/</a><br />\n<br />\n港大民研 (可以研究柒婆應唔應該落地獄!)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.pori.hk/donation\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pori.hk%2Fdonation&d=Xf5vvBv8GY7fsWMyNBE0dtagwJJ%2BwSr9lfhZhsTZPo0%3D&h=8fb5e073\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.pori.hk/donation</a><br />\n<br />\n仲有蘋果 網頁版好快課到3蚊<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">要將功補過既人快幫手貼有用既post黎回覆</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"35b267db0c2bd23f1b0d82cbff6bb910169b85ed","tid":1298341,"uid":105976,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T00:33:05.000Z","msg":"唔好諗住一句道歉就得  你睇柒婆道歉冇人要<br />\n要既係真正行動"},{"pid":"e3f40058e8fa22eef0a7ca34ae2b3b9677188ad4","tid":1298341,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T00:35:36.000Z","msg":"最新白宮聯署！要求美國國會立即通過《香港人權民主法案》<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1295654/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1295654/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"bc2ad1dec7f604c62af31fd06d15ecf48c3bf4e7","tid":1298341,"uid":61520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T00:36:06.000Z","msg":"港共成功左 由得我地和平遊行<br />\n<br />\n你地開始玩膠，即係證明你地不再憤怒，覺得好開心<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1298176\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1298176</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"48452517130c81df9e45be54e7da14904144e775","tid":1298341,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T00:36:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/asset